item.title: Error while adding in specials
item.dc:creator: @bryanc Bryanc
item.description:
@bryanc wrote:

It’s probably where it says: offsetY

make it like: offSetY

Coding is case sensitive. Try that, and usually the second word in a line of code or two words connected is capital like I show above.
